segmentosSRT.text: Fengxia's growing up. Another's on the way.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_02

segmentosSRT.text:
Why don't you go home?
There'll be other times.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_02

segmentosSRT.text: I hit him for not obeying.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_02

segmentosSRT.text: I'll hit him again if I have to.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_02

segmentosSRT.text: Sit then. Right in front of me!
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_02

segmentosSRT.text: You have to get rid of those puppets.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_02

segmentosSRT.text: Red Guards are swarming over the place.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_02

segmentosSRT.text:
I just caught them on a ladder,
pulling off roof tiles.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_02

segmentosSRT.text: You've gone to so much trouble.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_02

segmentosSRT.text: We've been through the valley of death.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_02

segmentosSRT.text:
- Sorry for the trouble.
- It's our job.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_02

segmentosSRT.text:
- Already?
- We didn't hear a sound.
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_02

segmentosSRT.text: Did he eat all seven buns?
segmentosSRT.speaker: SPEAKER_02
